Từ điển Anh - Việt
◘['gɔdis]
*danh từ
 ■nữ thần

Anh - Anh
goddess
■ noun
1》 a female deity.
2》 a woman who is greatly admired, especially for her beauty.

sentences.en: This temple was built in honor of the goddess Isis over two thousand years ago.
